data.text:
Princess Amelie of Yugoslavia (born Princess Amelie of Sweden on 1 October 1992) is a member of the Yugoslavian Royal Family as the wife of Prince Philip of Yugoslavia. She is also a member of the Sweddish Royal Family as the daughter of Carl XVI Gustaf, King of Sweden and Theresa, Princess Royal.
